[[Listen to Mama's voice->event3]]


:: Call for help {"position":"475,1325","size":"100,100"}
=><=

<img src="images/blowout.png" alt="flashlight beam on a shredded tire on an empty road at night">

(set: $calledHelp to true)

(if: $defiance >= 1)[(set: $heat to $heat + 2)]
(else:)[(set: $heat to $heat + 1)]

You pull your phone out and call RACV.

(enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["this still counts as laying low…"]

As you wait, the reality of being stuck settles in.

Whatever happens next, it won’t be on your time.

(if: $heat >= 2)[(set: $riskState to "high")]
(else-if: $heat >= 1)[(set: $riskState to "medium")]
(else:)[(set: $riskState to "low")]

