:: Get out of the car {"position":"600,1200","size":"100,100"}
=><=

You inspect the damage and quite frankly, you don't know what you're looking at. All you know is that the tires fucked and you have no spare. 

Opening the door, you slump back into the drivers seat, hazards blinking

The road is empty in both directions.

Officers about 15km from where you came...

And the next best stop is another 30...


[[Call for help->Call for help]]
[[Try to handle it yourself->Try to handle it yourself]]



:: Light a cigarette? {"position":"525,800","size":"100,100"}
=><=

(set: $coping to "deny")
<img src="images/cigarette.png" alt="close-up of a cigarette ember in a dark car interior">

(if: $defiance >= 1)[
You flick the lighter too close.
The flame sears your skin before the cigarette catches.
You hiss, shaking your hand as pain shoots up your fingers.

You take a deep drag, exhaling through your nose, trying to make sense of what happened.
]

=><=

(else-if: $authority >= 1)[
You think about lighting one — then don’t.
Your hands are steady. Your chest isn’t.
You put the cigarette back in the pack.
]

=><=
(else-if: $compliance >= 1)[
You light it carefully.
The cigarette flares, smoke filling your lungs as your shoulders finally drop.
You take a deep drag, exhaling through your nose, eyes forward like you’re still being watched.
]

=><=
(else:)[
You light it on the second try.

]

[["Jesus I gotta get a grip"->event3]]


:: Reach for your wallet {"position":"1225,450","size":"100,100"}
=><=

You comply, avoiding eye contact with the officer. 

You reach into your bag for your wallet. As you take it out, something slips and lands against the seat — a bracelet you recognize instantly. 

*"Shit"*

The officer’s gaze lingers for a moment as you open your wallet, and hand the piece of plastic to them, eyes fixed to the dotted lines ahead. 


The officer swiftly hands it back and waves you forward.


[/[Continue driving? ->event2]]


