=><=

(set: $reputation to $reputation + 0)
(set: $compliance to $compliance + 1)

You reach slowly for your wallet, keeping your eyes forward.

The officer watches every movement, then relaxes slightly.

|officer>["Thank you."]

(set: $checkpointState to "compliant")
[[Continue->event2]]



