:: arrival {"position":"600,1450","size":"100,100"}
=><=

<img src="images/farmhouse.png" alt="a farmhouse with one light on at night, long driveway">

hours later, the road takes you back.

the tyre is replaced. the car runs again.

you find the turnoff from her last message like it’s been waiting for you.

a farmhouse. one porch light. everything else swallowed by trees.

the gravel under your tyres sounds too loud.

(set: $ending to "")

(if: $riskState is "high")[
  (set: $ending to "storm")
]
(else-if: $checkpointState is "defiant")[
  (set: $ending to "storm")
]
(else-if: $coping is "reachout")[
  (set: $ending to "reunion")
]
(else-if: $coping is "deny")[
  (set: $ending to "silence")
]
(else:)[
  (set: $ending to "uncertain")
]

(if: $ending is "storm")[
  <img src="images/storm.png" alt="on the porch, she confronts mufudzi in the doorway">

  you walk up to the door already angry, still carrying the stop in your chest.
  the porch light catches your face and you hate how exposed it feels.

  mufudzi opens the door and you don’t step forward. you don’t smile.

  (enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
  |player>["what did you do?"]

  she flinches, then hardens like you just proved her right.
]
(else-if: $ending is "reunion")[
  <img src="images/reunion.png" alt="two sisters hugging under the porch light">

  you chew on your lip, waiting for her to respond to your knock.
  the door opens.

  mufudzi’s eyes go wide and then she’s pulling you in so fast you nearly trip.
  she’s shaking. you are too. but you’re here.

  (enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
  |player>["i’m here. i’m here."]
]
(else-if: $ending is "silence")[
  <img src="images/silence.png" alt="she hesitates on the porch while mufudzi watches from the doorway">

  you sit in the car longer than you mean to.
  the porch light waits. the door waits. you wait.

  when you finally step out, the cold hits you like a slap.
  mufudzi opens the door and you just… stand there.

  you had words the whole drive.
  now they won’t come.
]
(else:)[
  <img src="images/uncertain.png" alt="mufudzi in the doorway, distant headlights behind her">

  the door opens.

  mufudzi looks past you, into the dark, like she’s counting the spaces between headlights.

  (enchant:?mufudzi, (text-style:"italic"))
  |mufudzi>["did they follow you?"]

  you don’t know how to answer.
]



:: event1 {"position":"575,250","size":"100,100"}
=><=

<img src="images/pullover.png" alt="transportation officer at driver window, pulled over on the left shoulder">

You finally see another human being but you immediately want to turn around. Traffic slows suddenly, funneling cars into a narrow lane marked by cones and signs you don't want to see.


(enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["Oh, fuck me, man."]

A transportation officer steps forward and gestures for you to pull over. 

You pull over, exhaling slowly as you come to a stop. 

Rolling the window down, they approach your car...

(enchant:?officer, (text-style:"italic"))
|officer>["...Good evening ma'am, just after your drivers license please."]

[[Ask what this is about, calmly->AskCalm]]
[[Snap back, irritated->AskRude]]
[[Reach for your wallet without a word->SilentCompliance]]


:: event2 {"position":"575,550","size":"100,100"}
=><=

The checkpoint disappears in your rearview mirror, but your grip on the wheel doesn’t loosen.

You replay the interaction in your head. 

The officer’s tone.

The way they looked at you. 


 (enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
  
  |player>["He knew who I was...didn't he?"] 


If something goes wrong, it won’t just affect you...

[[Light a cigarette->Light a cigarette?]]
[[Call Mama->Call Mama]]
[["What if I've fucked everything?"->"What if I've fucked everything?"]]
[["Everything is fine"]] 


:: event3 {"position":"600,1000","size":"100,100"}
=><=

(if: $authority >= 1)[
You keep both hands on the wheel, jaw tight. 

(text-style: "rumble") + (text-size: 2)[BANG]

]
(else:)[
As you flick the butt out the window, the sound comes without warning.

(text-style: "rumble") + (text-size: 2)[BANG]

]

A sharp noise rings throughout your skull, the steering wheel jerking in your hands. Tears spring to your eyes.

Fear.

Exhaustion.

You try to keep it together but you can't even keep the car on the road. 
You fight the car into the emergency stopping lane as you hear the rubber flapping.

Everything comes to a stop and you lick the tears from your lips. 

(enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["I can't do this..." ]

[[Get out of the car]]


