=><=
 ###nothing out of the ordinary 
 
 <img src="images/intro.png" alt="driving at dusk on an empty road, right-hand drive car">

The neverending road stretches ahead of you, 100kms of absolute nothing, knuckles whitening at the wheel. You keep the air con blasting on your fingertips to keep you awake. 

It’s been days since you last heard from your sister, Mufudzi, and her last message still echoes in your head. 

(enchant:?Mufudzi, (text-style:"italic"))

|Mufudzi>[ "For the better..."

"For the better...."]

You hear it again, like she’s in the car with you.

She said she was safe. that you would see her soon — but to lay low.

…and not tell a soul.


You want to believe her — even if nothing about her disappearance feels right.

She said it would all make sense soon. “For the better,” she promised.

---

 
[[Keep driving ->event1]]




:: outro {"position":"750,1575","size":"100,100"}
=><=
(if: $calledHelp)[
Your phone feels heavier in your hand than it should.
Each time a car passes by, you flinch.
]

The road is quiet again.

Somewhere ahead, your sister is waiting.

For now, all you can do is sit with the choices you’ve made — and just pray they were the right ones.

  (enchant:?player, (text-style:"italic"))
|player>["Oh Mufudzi, what did you get yourself into?"]


